    "cff_info": "<div id=\"fieldInfoPTE2\" style=\" margin-top: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 10px; border-radius: 5px;\">\n  <h4>PTE Predictive Nomogram (2)</h4>\n  <p><i>Lin et al., 2022</i></p>\n  <p><b>DOI:</b> <a href=\"https://doi.org/10.1038/s4159802224824z\" target=\"_blank\">10.1038/s4159802224824z</a></p>\n  <h4>Factors and Points</h4>\n  <ul>\n    <li><b>Contusion Site:</b>\n      <ul>\n        <li>0 points: Occipital</li>\n        <li>14 points: Parietal</li>\n        <li>73 points: Frontal</li>\n        <li>79 points: Temporal</li>\n        <li>100 points: Multiple sites</li>\n      </ul>\n    </li>\n    <li><b>Chronic Alcohol Use:</b>\n      <ul>\n        <li>0 points: No</li>\n        <li>28 points: Yes</li>\n      </ul>\n    </li>\n    <li><b>Contusion Volume:</b>\n      <ul>\n        <li>0 points: ≤13.5 ml</li>\n        <li>61 points: >13.5 ml</li>\n      </ul>\n    </li>\n    <li><b>Skull Fracture:</b>\n      <ul>\n        <li>0 points: No</li>\n        <li>24 points: Linear</li>\n        <li>78 points: Depressed</li>\n      </ul>\n    </li>\n    <li><b>Subdural Hematoma (SDH):</b>\n      <ul>\n        <li>0 points: No</li>\n        <li>49 points: Yes</li>\n      </ul>\n    </li>\n    <li><b>Glasgow Coma Scale (GCS) Score:</b>\n      <ul>\n        <li>0 points: Mild (13-15)</li>\n        <li>22 points: Moderate (9-12)</li>\n        <li>95 points: Severe (3-8)</li>\n      </ul>\n    </li>\n    <li><b>Non-Late Post-Traumatic Seizures (Non-LPTS):</b>\n      <ul>\n        <li>0 points: No</li>\n        <li>76 points: Yes</li>\n      </ul>\n    </li>\n  </ul>\n  <h4>Risk Estimates</h4>\n  <p>Predicted risk of epilepsy after 2 years based on the score:</p>\n  <table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr style=\"background-color: #f2f2f2;\">\n        <th style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">Score</th>\n        <th style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">Risk</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">131</td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">1%</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">167</td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">5%</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">184</td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">10%</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">194</td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">15%</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">201</td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">20%</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">208</td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">25%</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">213</td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">30%</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">218</td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">35%</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">223</td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">40%</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">227</td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">45%</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">231</td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">50%</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">236</td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">55%</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">240</td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">60%</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">245</td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">65%</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">250</td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">70%</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">255</td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">75%</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">262</td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">80%</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">269</td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">85%</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">279</td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">90%</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">296</td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">95%</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">332</td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">99%</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n  <h4>Additional Study Information</h4>\n  <table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 10px;\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr style=\"background-color: #f2f2f2;\">\n        <th style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">Category</th>\n        <th style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">Details</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\"><b>Population</b></td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">Derivation: 457 patients (Qinghai Provincial People’s Hospital, 2016-2019).</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\"><b>Statistical Methods</b></td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">Univariate and multivariate logistic regression.</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\"><b>Performance Metrics</b></td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">C-index: 0.9829 (high predictive power).</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\"><b>Generalizability</b></td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">Moderate (limited by single-center study).</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\"><b>Clinical Utility</b></td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">Identifies high-risk patients for targeted anti-seizure medication (ASM) treatment or prophylaxis.</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</div>",
    "authors": "Lin S, Wang Q, Zhu Y, et al.",
    "journal": "Scientific Reports",
    "year": 2022,
    "clinical_utility": "Post-traumatic epilepsy (PTE) is an important cause of poor prognosis in patients with cerebral contusions. The primary purpose of this study is to evaluate the high-risk factors of PTE by summarizing and analyzing the baseline data, laboratory examination, and imaging features of patients with a cerebral contusion, and then developing a Nomogram prediction model and validating it.",
    "outcome": "Establishment and validation of PTE prediction model in patients with cerebral contusion"
  },
